        <dc:description>&lt;p&gt;Roshar is a world of stone and storms. Uncanny tempests of incredible power sweep across the rocky terrain so frequently that they have shaped ecology and civilization alike.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It has been centuries since the fall of the ten consecrated orders known as the Knights Radiant, but their Shardblades and Shardplate remain.&lt;/p&gt;</dc:description>
